    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. Discretization error factor exceeds MRL 2 threshold (GCI 2.1% vs 5% criterion). Output comparison within 15% acceptance band with conservative systematic bias. Credibility evidence package supports regulatory submission claim that CFD model is adequate to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB COU.",
